# AI-Driven Product Recommendation System

This project demonstrates a simple collaborative filtering-based recommendation system.

## Setup

1. Clone the repository.
2. Install dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`.
3. Run the app: `python run.py`.

## API

`GET /recommend/<user_id>`: Returns product recommendations for a given user ID.

How to Run the Project
Install Dependencies: Install the required packages using pip:

bash
Copy code
pip install -r requirements.txt
Run the Application: Start the Flask application by running:

bash
Copy code
python run.py
Access the Recommendation API: Once the app is running, you can access the recommendation system by visiting:

bash
Copy code
http://127.0.0.1:5000/recommend/1
This will return recommendations for User 1.

